div.div:
Create PresenceEditor class and update various files
This commit introduces the new PresenceEditor class for user authorization in Broadcasting and modifies DeleteOldSales command by removing 'deleted_at' update in Console. It also enhances quill.blade.php view by adding slug data attribute and revises the animation effect in dashy.js.

Integrate Bootstrap5 theme with FullCalendar and update Pusher authentication
This commit adds the Bootstrap5 theme to the FullCalendar, improving its visual coherence, and adjusts Pusher library settings for better authentication management. These updates result in an improved calendar interface and enhanced application functionality. Calendar styles and the webpack.mix.js file have also been modified to accommodate these changes.

Add configuration management in dashy.js
This commit adds new parsers and controller mappings, extending theme and asset management functionality in dashy.js. It includes Gitignore preferences, 'user_theme' configuration methods, and adds 'shipu/themevel' to composer.json for improved theme and asset support. This update also introduces support for PSR4 namespaces 'Shipu\\Themevel\\' and 'Noodlehaus\\'.

Add new files for configuration management and extend functionality
This commit incorporates new parsers, controller mappings, and extends support for theme and asset management. It also includes extended Gitignore preferences and methods for 'user_theme' configuration. Addition of 'shipu/themevel' to composer.json gives improved support for themes and assets while introducing support for PSR4 namespaces 'Shipu\\Themevel\\' and 'Noodlehaus\\'.

Update vendor.js file and refactor layout properties
Updated the vendor.js.LICENSE file to include copyright information for the Pusher JS Library. The CalendarLayout in the Orchid Layouts was also refactored, removing the description property and adding a slug property instead. An additional change was made to formatting in the confirm.blade.php partial view.

Refactor animation property in dashy.js
Updated the animation attribute in dashy.js file under vendor/fluffici. The change enhances the flow and consistency of animations by adjusting animation duration timings.
